;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;丹麦首相梅特·弗雷德里克森 (Mette Frederiksen)&lt;/strong&gt;认为，恢复对国内最富有居民征收财产税的提议将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/oI3dO2sHZU6b_tmpUWptv5fi6PAapU-4gb2JLajI12jGC5LB-fOxlXxuD0dlyNwa1zHKiL8qT-LQfZ2_-6bgU5lEtdIZ1hSrk9JqZ6yeiiA8BvJiKO8EjkKH1c5kpm72jqfx5lhYQLsSOVPBV8IOHGkeoQmU8MTB8FRNxAD7PNXK__Jnpudt9aORfZLRwqaiKYdG-nI9PO5JK6VRDKSmw0nD8ukNJiFvThcAZanPBRrWYAJOm3_HgC2d8HjjWeAP4wRLTK3K83LdtbVTTRseVo4e_b6GQu5mzvFn-0wV3F-ND2DB_MoIDecY1vlWNaa-4bsR-afWqAddAiYI85VqOllZdY7u75yaNZeqd2qy3N_jRP94Q-nDjWtjxVeXpPTV8w6yJkNKpfZUS6WaHP7cr2E04wGZUMEfsialCJ7lpDEBD84rR8006jSn_XDtau4m-UrjXsAm8t9-NzWpoJtdwunjb_OPSb5Duc12WP1WOpMUwEgz145vi_wu4RBLRxb_i6YBFgPSX6Pdf1loj-U8LDJLu4AyNxBn/TAz2ot51oAq3rTV_DAEuNtbTEFd7EsTV/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="丹麦首相押注 10 亿美元财富税以保住工作"&gt;引起选民的共鸣&lt;/a&gt;，并有助于她下个月继续掌权，尽管批评者称这可能会导致亿万富翁大量外流。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;雷切尔·里夫斯(Rachel Reeves)将于下周低调发布&lt;/strong&gt;有关英国经济状况的最新消息，她试图在最近两年一次的财政事件之前的无休止的投机循环中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/-z2FQHI7k2Xsu2KxcDEp8CHzApZFmkq_rNUS5WI3M2tcGuh3xssvhbJfijryw4qUMwZ87RTfs7OEoh68lbXmj6KbjSHgnRbLiuqXlPbYcNRCtwK2GcnWBG92t97ioZfitvY17dh0kvApR-bOLl_0kVS34RIgonmXrr7MXS9WP2oVNDe7v1e6hziGnBGj-OXdPc07ioDA928bSjgySiKZUPiaV6oJDtcyxTcH4SMQNouhbvI_3bfLyMeIoJV5M4dRw8-UYqkZ8IZfm4rMVt6m7LzBmTIQL28lbK4AWl7VajerjMClCAtkSz3KPJPaOA43s_3eMNa6X5xYNUty2uzH6Nds8RGDZzB_Sa0EG04fKJLqvIViPi7-UldF2tIIzctPuMYxBI2LMytFxF-QitC04gJOqhSaQrQOC4VOgltrLIUe5kkFBdPS0VAY8M69_UNtOoLjuZHifd3AcgxPNt_8IGDJxdhHaoN1fRihFBgYoRgscJWswvlRfOJseoKnwNoTy4eqpls0AzApYrkh0640/3Hc2RqMrDU00o7AfbHW0WdFnN9OzR1pk/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="里夫斯旨在通过低调的经济更新来结束英国税务争论"&gt;划清界限&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;不要错