inks.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/cOuS6CaKs3scoM-iKFIOFBk0G4nmV0GNGDbLc33B8QbanOiTQ2sxm12nC3w_4bOshsz6zN-Rx12TjFvrAo5hS9OuSbrnU9Y7OIbDyF7tWot0Sbgs37zl5nJGQKCesHXdU6A_vJlKLa8zaotYrTuNHzgOfSXdTdvrBBFEMZwFeJP5dRYcofM4cuTfpjcI1xk7L3vsU5Lqv_rzH338twITCIRLxKE1ArmpysFVcSN0iR0ucdsH23hrBDtJ2Exvt7NvDzU-mWMURT5aTatDj4U6HTRFL5AtQkpBxHKb-jIUn2OyrcOg-NgiUJPUtL5YMEcsPX5jL3BJlEqoGI8k0oj5AX2GkN_0srW5SHvCnxmwNVsrK1i3foZq7UUBrsZ-IAnwnm5SFxeaXsIqEVjpDcvS3kfwVbTnBL-SO3bgoX9xDXKnwyrUrce9WKOdd0U6qp1q-hPBVA-vnrpqxZ7AxFOlOtsURNJWzkTDQjyK3t_QtRH8BR2aPC5_ipui4ywhdY8GF9BQhHpad5IyKz7DjQ/Jw-hEgDgVUg5QtQ7LnNoUNAon_ucJqRa/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="人民币兑欧元开始升值之际，默茨访华"&gt;开始升值&lt;/a&gt;。尽管人民币兑美元汇率上涨，但中国受到严格控制的货币兑欧元汇率去年仍下跌约8%，这是自2003年以来的最大跌幅，推动了中国对欧洲的大量出口，并促使柏林指责中国企业相对于德国同行享有优势。默茨表示，他将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/tHGK-4JP4CMzpcAL4-HX6uuFGuCooLUUYJEgw_oQ9_sX9yL6rXIjz2DqA0qvQM6BNtlslBBnHrALK23UXRVgex52XkBRJ3V18Qb29dqU_VjhvazGnZHejg7_4mQuyLFRxlnsWoTwu_ftLC0l412jeF5yo1KnKm-zfbo6vdzV4AiQU6FCZUqZ5dTDg88VROUSZC3NxnaRvMy5iNyRgKTKBLXvp4wwLx_nE4Lmrz3ar5d4X_s1SyOTcGSP2N5QrlF_pGUJRq3abTnBRb6r-Zwij4XppCeyvdU814FbgnvJHE53gM89WUWblPGWuTJPCSzYt2Z6VXS5QY8o-c8VOYGLx3kooV3KLtm_Wp1zpOmn38fe-J3m0oRbnLIx4VBa2Jj6-DYvlJ4Z1FmkvEmS9M5-Vj77sstCNkwqhK0eK3yXstdaJSq7UcDIC5AamNnAM6BaNS6A6J5TrHlDhbjwfMwTS3ErIsVBd01damBRRHlpA7g-wASo1uyDfmfU7FIy4RjkdivjhReZZYCeT_yYVrxaCvY/tOzfHjVx9Dk4HQcba90yh9g6mK0n6g7u/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="默茨作为总理首次访华承诺加强与中国的关系"&gt;继续努力&lt;/a&gt;加强中德关系。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;最后&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;自2019年特朗普第一任期内的一次高调外交失败以来，朝鲜与美国的关系一直处于深度冻结状态。现在，金正恩刚刚结束了在平壤举行的为期7天的执政党代表大会，并提出了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/_BJFAC95kxPMM5G8hMQBqBQA-7bB3VY36hAedZW8grN54aX3ygrqRfvLt2DHo6qGD-HbL9w9